title: The Promise Is In You | Joel Osteen

description:
God has equipped you with everything you need to reach your destiny. Get ready to rise to new levels as you stir up the gifts He gave you. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
